2026-06-14 22:32:41.481  INFO [http-nio-8080-exec-1] c.a.e.b.t.i.HttpExecutor                 : HttpExecutor call resp: {"data":{"pageSize":20,"pageNo":1,"totalSize":1,"totalPage":0,"resultList":[{"id":2136,"accountId":3,"gmailMessageId":"19eb01e4b8679303","gmailThreadId":"19e73ef65323871a","fromAddress":"Sinchen <sinaphonix6@gmail.com>","toAddresses":"Psylos1 Offical <info@psylos1.com>","subject":"Re: New customer message on 29 May 2026 at 09:32","bodyText":"","bodyHtml":"<html class=\"apple-mail-supports-explicit-dark-mode\"><head><meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body dir=\"auto\">Just to let you know, I put the two items, the pants and the top in one package.<br id=\"lineBreakAtBeginningOfSignature\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Von meinem iPhone gesendet</div><div dir=\"ltr\"><br><blockquote type=\"cite\">Am 07.06.2026 um 06:03 schrieb Psylos1 Offical &lt;info@psylos1.com&gt;:<br><br></blockquote></div><blockquote type=\"cite\"><div dir=\"ltr\">﻿<div dir=\"ltr\">Dear&nbsp;Sinchen,<br><br>Thank you for the information you provided. After the subsequent warehouse receives the goods, they will verify the item information. Once it is confirmed to be correct, they will proceed with the next step for you.<br><br>Thank you for your understanding and cooperation.<br><br>Best regards,<br>Psylos 1-Eric</div><br><div class=\"gmail_quote gmail_quote_container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_attr\">On Sat, Jun 6, 2026 at 9:51 PM Sinchen &lt;<a href=\"mailto:sinaphonix6@gmail.com\">sinaphonix6@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br></div><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 0.8ex;border-left:1px solid rgb(204,204,204);padding-left:1ex\"><div dir=\"auto\">Greetings,<div><br></div><div>I send the package with the courier DHL. The Tracking Number is&nbsp;<span style=\"color:rgb(26,26,26);font-family:&quot;NOLP PKDS Delivery&quot;,Delivery,sans-serif;font-size:14.875px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255)\">CY734876983DE</span></div><div><font color=\"#1a1a1a\" face=\"NOLP PKDS Delivery, Delivery, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.875px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255)\"><br></span></font></div><div><font color=\"#1a1a1a\" face=\"NOLP PKDS Delivery, Delivery, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.875px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255)\">Thank you!<br id=\"m_-6726546939723216941lineBreakAtBeginningOfSignature\"></span></font><div dir=\"ltr\">Von meinem iPhone gesendet</div><div dir=\"ltr\"><br><blockquote type=\"cite\">Am 04.06.2026 um 09:31 schrieb Psylos1 Offical &lt;<a href=\"mailto:info@psylos1.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@psylos1.com</a>&gt;:<br><br></blockquote></div><blockquote type=\"cite\"><div dir=\"ltr\">﻿<div dir=\"ltr\"><div>Dear&nbsp;Sinchen,</div><div><br></div>Here is the returning address:<br>Contact: MuMu(木木)<br>Phone:13082824982<br>Address: 5th Floor, No. 38 Jianji Road, Suoqian Town, Xiaoshan District<br>Province:Zhe jiang<br>City: Hang zhou &nbsp;<br>Country:China<br><br>Look forward to your reply.<br><br>Best regards,<br>Psylos 1-Eric</div><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\"><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_attr\">On Thu, Jun 4, 2026 at 3:22 PM Sinchen &lt;<a href=\"mailto:sinaphonix6@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">sinaphonix6@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br></div><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 0.8ex;border-left:1px solid rgb(204,204,204);padding-left:1ex\"><div dir=\"auto\">I did not send it back to you, since I don’t know the address to send it back.<br id=\"m_-6726546939723216941m_7647324955095603930lineBreakAtBeginningOfSignature\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Von meinem iPhone gesendet</div><div dir=\"ltr\"><br><blockquote type=\"cite\">Am 04.06.2026 um 09:15 schrieb Psylos1 Offical &lt;<a href=\"mailto:info@psylos1.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@psylos1.com</a>&gt;:<br><br></blockquote></div><blockquote type=\"cite\"><div dir=\"ltr\">﻿<div dir=\"ltr\">Dear Sinchen,<br><br>Thank you for your confirmation.<br><br>We just wanted to kindly follow up — have you already arranged to send the item(s) back to us?<br><br>If you have already shipped the package, could you please provide us with the return tracking number? If you have not yet shipped it, please let us know as well so we can assist you further if needed.<br><br>Thank you for your cooperation and understanding.<br><br>Best regards,<br>Psylos1 Spring</div><div dir=\"ltr\"><br></div><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\"><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_attr\">On Mon, Jun 1, 2026 at 6:31 PM Sinchen &lt;<a href=\"mailto:sinaphonix6@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">sinaphonix6@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br></div><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 0.8ex;border-left:1px solid rgb(204,204,204);padding-left:1ex\"><div dir=\"auto\">I confirm, to send it back&nbsp;<br id=\"m_-6726546939723216941m_7647324955095603930m_-6565784446435057062m_1098986311850455959lineBreakAtBeginningOfSignature\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Von meinem iPhone gesendet</div><div dir=\"ltr\"><br><blockquote type=\"cite\">Am 01.06.2026 um 12:12 schrieb Psylos1 Offical &lt;<a href=\"mailto:info@psylos1.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@psylos1.com</a>&gt;:<br><br></blockquote></div><blockquote type=\"cite\"><div dir=\"ltr\">﻿<div dir=\"ltr\">Dear&nbsp;Sinchen,<br><br>Thank you for shopping with Psylos1. We’ve received your exchange request and are here to assist you.<br><br>Before proceeding, please review our return policy:<br><br>Return Window: We offer a 14-day return policy. Please ensure that you have not exceeded 14 days since receiving the item. Unfortunately, returns outside this period cannot be accepted.<br>Item Condition: Items must be unworn, unused, with original tags, and in their original packaging to qualify for a return.<br>Return Shipping: Customers are responsible for the return shipping fee for non-merchant-related reasons, such as size exchanges or personal preferences.<br><br>The following information is extremely important. Please read it carefully.<br>1. Return process: Please return the item to the designated address in China (the specific information will be provided to you after you confirm the exchange). The international shipping cost, customs duties and other related expenses incurred during the return process will be borne by you. Please estimate the shipping cost first and choose the most economical shipping method.<br>2. Customs clearance fees: To ensure that your returned package can be received by our company smoothly and quickly, we hereby remind you: It is necessary for me to inform you that the declared value of the package is directly related to the possible customs clearance fees or import duties. Generally speaking, the higher the declared value, the higher the possible customs clearance fees will be.<br>You can declare a reasonable value based on the actual value of the goods. However, please note that the customs department has the right to request proof of the value, or if they believe that the declared amount does not match the content of the goods, they may make adjustments. After the item is returned to China, customs clearance fees (such as customs duties, value-added tax, etc.) may be incurred. These fees will also be borne by you. Once we receive the returned item and confirm it is correct, we will generate a customs clearance fee bill for you. After you complete the payment, we will proceed with the exchange process.<br>3. Exchange arrangement: After we receive the returned item and you have paid the customs clearance fees, we will process the exchange order for you. To avoid additional costs or delays, please ensure the item is in good condition and complies with the return policy. <br><br>If the item is not returned in its original condition, we may be unable to process the exchange.<br>We appreciate your cooperation and understanding.<br>Here is the returning address:<br>Contact: MuMu(木木)<br>Phone:13082824982<br>Address: 5th Floor, No. 38 Jianji Road, Suoqian Town, Xiaoshan District<br>Province:Zhe jiang <br>City: Hang zhou &nbsp;<br>Country:China<br><br>Look forward to your reply.<br><br>Best regards,<br>Psylos 1-Eric</div><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\"><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_attr\">On Mon, Jun 1, 2026 at 4:07 AM Sinchen &lt;<a href=\"mailto:sinaphonix6@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\">sinaphonix6@gmail.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br></div><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 0.8ex;border-left:1px solid rgb(204,204,204);padding-left:1ex\"><div dir=\"auto\">I confirm to send it back.<br id=\"m_-6726546939723216941m_7647324955095603930m_-6565784446435057062m_1098986311850455959m_160364898500314825lineBreakAtBeginningOfSignature\"><div dir=\"ltr\">Von meinem iPhone gesendet</div><div dir=\"ltr\"><br><blockquote type=\"cite\">Am 31.05.2026 um 21:26 schrieb Psylos1 Offical &lt;<a href=\"mailto:info@psylos1.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@psylos1.com</a>&gt;:<br><br></blockquote></div><blockquote type=\"cite\"><div dir=\"ltr\">﻿<div dir=\"ltr\">Dear Sina,<br><br>Thank you for shopping with Psylos1. We’ve received your exchange request and are here to assist you.<br><br>Before proceeding, please review our return policy:<br><br>Return Window: We offer a 14-day return policy. Please ensure that you have not exceeded 14 days since receiving the item. Unfortunately, returns outside this period cannot be accepted.<br>Item Condition: Items must be unworn, unused, with original tags, and in their original packaging to qualify for a return.<br>Return Shipping: Customers are responsible for the return shipping fee for non-merchant-related reasons, such as size exchanges or personal preferences.<br><br>The following information is extremely important. Please read it carefully.<br>1. Return process: Please return the item to the designated address in China (the specific information will be provided to you after you confirm the exchange). The international shipping cost, customs duties and other related expenses incurred during the return process will be borne by you. Please estimate the shipping cost first and choose the most economical shipping method.<br>2. Customs clearance fees: To ensure that your returned package can be received by our company smoothly and quickly, we hereby remind you: It is necessary for me to inform you that the declared value of the package is directly related to the possible customs clearance fees or import duties. Generally speaking, the higher the declared value, the higher the possible customs clearance fees will be.<br>You can declare a reasonable value based on the actual value of the goods. However, please note that the customs department has the right to request proof of the value, or if they believe that the declared amount does not match the content of the goods, they may make adjustments. After the item is returned to China, customs clearance fees (such as customs duties, value-added tax, etc.) may be incurred. These fees will also be borne by you. Once we receive the returned item and confirm it is correct, we will generate a customs clearance fee bill for you. After you complete the payment, we will proceed with the exchange process.<br>3. Exchange arrangement: After we receive the returned item and you have paid the customs clearance fees, we will process the exchange order for you. To avoid additional costs or delays, please ensure the item is in good condition and complies with the return policy. <br><br>If you confirm that you want to proceed, please reply to inform us and we will send you the detailed return address and instructions.<br><br>Sincerely yours, &nbsp;<br>Psylos 1-Eric</div><br><div class=\"gmail_quote\"><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_attr\">On Fri, May 29, 2026 at 9:32 PM PSYLOS 1 (Shopify) &lt;<a href=\"mailto:mailer@shopify.com\" target=\"_blank\">mailer@shopify.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br></div><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 0.8ex;border-left:1px solid rgb(204,204,204);padding-left:1ex\"><div><u></u>\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    \r\n      \r\n    \r\n    \r